# [PATCHED CLASS] HunYuanMoEV1Experts
# Original class replaced with: PatchedHunYuanMoEV1Experts
# Reason: Route MoE experts through the VeOmni fused/EP OpSlot with an eager fallback
# Source: veomni.models.transformers.hunyuan_image_3.hunyuan_image_3_gpu_patch_gen_config
